Registration Results

reg_test_df <- reg_test_df %>%
    mutate(tvec_1_diff = reg_results_1.tvec_1 - reg_results_2.tvec_1,
           tvec_2_diff = reg_results_1.tvec_2 - reg_results_2.tvec_2,
           r_diff_norm = sqrt(tvec_1_diff**2 + tvec_2_diff**2)
    ) %>%
    select(strain, batch, aqsettings, date, FoV_id, tvec_1_diff, tvec_2_diff, r_diff_norm, experiment)

function includes finding the standard deviation for the components of the translation vector difference (tvec_diff_1 and tvec_diff_2 or (\(\sigma_{y,diff}\) and \(\sigma_{x,diff}\))) and calculating the r_diff_precision (reg_diff_prec or \(\sigma_{reg}\))

reg_stat_sum_fn <- function(grouped_df){
    grouped_df %>% summarise(
        group_size = n(),
        tvec_1_diff_mean = mean(tvec_1_diff),
        tvec_1_diff_median = median(tvec_1_diff),
        tvec_1_diff_sd = sd(tvec_1_diff),
        tvec_2_diff_median = median(tvec_2_diff),
        tvec_2_diff_mean = mean(tvec_2_diff),
        tvec_2_diff_sd = sd(tvec_2_diff),
    # remember: r_diff_norm = sqrt(tvec_1_diff**2 + tvec_2_diff**2)
        r_diff_median = median(r_diff_norm), 
        r_diff_mean = mean(r_diff_norm),
        r_diff_sd = sd(r_diff_norm),
        r_diff_prec = sqrt(tvec_1_diff_sd**2 + tvec_2_diff_sd**2)
        )
}
reg_sum_by_exp_df <- reg_test_df %>%
    group_by(experiment) %>%
    reg_stat_sum_fn()

r_diff_prec_lookup_vector <- reg_sum_by_exp_df$r_diff_prec
names(r_diff_prec_lookup_vector) <- reg_sum_by_exp_df$experiment

reg_comp_by_exp_df <- reg_test_df %>%
  mutate(
    r_diff_prec = r_diff_prec_lookup_vector[experiment],
    r_diff_2sigma = 2 * r_diff_prec,
    r_diff_norm_vs_2sigma = r_diff_norm < r_diff_2sigma
  )
reg_sum_by_strain_df <- reg_test_df %>%
    group_by(strain) %>%
    reg_stat_sum_fn()

r_diff_prec_lookup_vector <- reg_sum_by_strain_df$r_diff_prec
names(r_diff_prec_lookup_vector) <- reg_sum_by_strain_df$strain

reg_comp_by_strain_df <- reg_test_df %>%
  mutate(
    r_diff_prec = r_diff_prec_lookup_vector[strain],
    r_diff_2sigma = 2 * r_diff_prec,
    r_diff_norm_vs_2sigma = r_diff_norm < r_diff_2sigma
  )

  )
